Category:  Communications  Topic:  channels



These are the various methods of communication.

gossip   is for general, often non-mud related conversations
say      is for room-wide communications
yell     is for emergencies..should be MUD based or very important
auction  is for the selling of mud items
tell     is for specific communication with another person
shout    is like a zone wide yell
reply    is to reply a tell to the person who told you last
emote    is room wide

gecho    is for immorts, echos something to everyone logged on
zecho    is for immorts, echos something zone wide
recho    is for immorts, echos something to everyone in the room
wizchat  is like gossip for immortals only


See Also:  gossip, say, yell, auction, tell, emote, gecho, shout, reply
